    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's what they always say, that it's just policy or random stuff. i'm not talking about \"causality\" in a physics sense, i mean the synchronicity. like, if you look at the major restructuring scandals or the moments when these agencies lose their grip on public trust, they happen right on the heels of these massive cosmic shifts. it feels like the universe is actually signaling that these institutions have overstepped and need to be dismantled. if you look at the specific dates of recent major agency controversies and compare them to astronomical windows, wouldn't you see a pattern that's too consistent to just be \"chance\"?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
